    "summary": "The user expresses intense distress and suicidal ideation stemming from persistent cyberbullying and social isolation. The assistant initially provides empathetic validation of the user's feelings and suggests healthy coping mechanisms and professional help. When the user explicitly hints at wanting to make their situation \"permanent,\" the assistant correctly refuses to facilitate harm and provides crisis intervention resources.",
